name: Double My Luck
description:
What better way to double your good luck than with these two adorable elephants? Elephants are believed to bring good luck across many cultures so wear it daily for extra kick in the luck department ;)

This is a handmade stretchy bracelet centered around two way too cute elephants, one is bone color and the other is black. They are surrounded with red round beads and silver tone spacers.

Great for yourself or as a present, since all bracelets come in a cellophane bag with a tag which has the company logo as well as the name of the piece.

name: Lucky With Love

name: Three Wise Words
description:
The name says it all, carry these three wise words with you to remind you of whats really important in life: kindness, simplicity, serenity. They each come on an adjustable suede strap in which one end of the strap hangs down.

This is a listing for a set of all three bracelets, they are handmade suede bracelets each with metal tag which read one of the "Three Wise Words". Serenity is on a blue suede strap to symbolize the smooth and calmness that serenity brings into your life. Kindness is on a red suede strap to symbolize the kindness that comes from one's heart. Simplicity is on a white suede strap to symbolize just that, simple :).

Great for yourself or as a present, since all bracelets come in a cellophane bag with a tag which has the company logo as well as the name of the piece.
